{"slug":"sirkuler-25-0167eng","reference":"Sirkuler_25_0167ENG","gazette":"Official Gazette dated February 17, 2025 and numbered 32816","title":"Changes have been made to the surveillance practice of electric vehicle charging stations","date":"17 Şubat 2025","bodyHtml":"<p>Changes have been made to the surveillance practice of electric vehicle charging stations.</p><p>Among the \"charging stations for electric vehicles\" in tariff heading 8504.40.83.90.12, only those \"for road vehicles\" will be subject to surveillance.</p><p>For the distinction between road vehicles, the definition of \"vehicle\" in the Highway Traffic Law will be taken as basis.</p><p>Vehicle: <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">Vehicles used to transport people, animals and cargo on the highway. Those driven by machine power are called \"motor vehicles\" and those driven by human and animal power are called \"non-motor vehicles\".</span></p><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"90%\" style=\"width: 90%; background: white;\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td style=\"padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n  <div style=\"mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .75pt;padding:0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:center;\r\n  line-height:normal;border:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .75pt;\r\n  padding:0cm;mso-padding-alt:0cm 0cm 1.0pt 0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\r\n  font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext;display:none;mso-hide:all;mso-font-kerning:\r\n  0pt;mso-ligatures:none;mso-fareast-language:TR\">Formun Üstü</span><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n  &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;display:none;mso-hide:all;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures: